CloseManagementGroupContextForm is a Form
    is primary
    propagate as a drill
    title is "CloseManagementGroup<CloseManagementGroup>"
    Layout
        three column distributed
            column1
                paragraph
                    CloseManagementGroup
                    Description
                        show up to 10 characters
            column2
                paragraph
                    CorporateCalendar
                        label is "DefaultCalendar"
                        show up to 10 characters
                    CorporateCalendar.Description
                        no label
                        display as text
                        show up to 10 characters
            column3
                paragraph
                    CorporatePeriodGroup
                        label is "DefaultPeriodGroup"
                        show up to 10 characters
                    CorporatePeriodGroup.Description
                        no label
                        display as text
                        show up to 10 characters
